# Explicit ts_dict_* aggregates switch the scan to term-dict rows, which would
# silently corrupt sibling document-row aggregates.
statement error
SELECT ts_dict_agg(cat) AS a, count(*) AS c FROM mc_idx
----
db error: ERROR: ts_dict_* aggregates cannot be combined with other aggregates over the same scan
HINT: compute the other aggregates in a separate subquery
